### Create admin user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin123",
  "enabled": true,
  "roleIds": [1]
}

###

### Create customer user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json


{
  "username": "customer",
  "email": "customer@example.com",
  "password": "customer123",
  "enabled": true,
  "roleIds": [2]
}